summary: An ordinance repealing Ordinance No. 76397, approved the 23rd day of October, 1947, as amended by Ordinance No. 76839, providing for the improvement of the Alley in Blocks 3 and 4, Replat of Blocks 3, 4, 5, 6 and 13 in Replat of Green Lake Home Addition, being the alley between East Green Lake Way and North 77th Street, from Corliss Avenue to Sunnyside Avenue, and certain other alleys, by paving and otherwise improving the same.
